cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with the problem of 3D reconstruction from a single image. It may also belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) category as it involves generating 3D point clouds. The use of deep neural networks for this task suggests that it may also be relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper's focus on designing a novel architecture, loss function, and learning paradigm suggests that it may also be relevant to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) category.
